channel.title: Eclipse-PvP (Cammy-PvP) Updated, New Models, Clan System, Nastalgic Feel [Delta]
channel.description:
[center][b][size=14pt]Cammy PvP/Eclipse PvP Release[/size][/b] -Intro- We all remember and love the Cammy PvP source, for me it holds a special place in my RsPs journey in that I think that it was a turning point on the way that people view Private Servers. Cammy PvP was one of the most fun servers I have played to this day. This source was a major throwback for me and I feel that I have done enough work to this server to where it could be competitively put online as a somewhat successful server. -Information- [b]-New Models have been added to the client ( Dragon Claws, AGS, Bandos Models, Godsword Models, Colored Whips ect. ) -Counting IP's for those who Multi Log for PKP or Killstreak Count -A new point Store using special Shop Values -75% Finished Pest Control ( Portal Re-spawning and the Pest Control Points/Point shop themselves are unfinished ) -Clan Creating, Clan Joining, Clan Leaving, and Clan Waring are all refurbished and working. -Cleaned out the Client.java file as it was disgusting ( remember this is a delta ) ( Deleted useless methods, Took out half of the skilling data as it is not needed, ect ) -Correct Animations for : Godswords, Claws, Whips, Most Dragon Weapons, also added specials to the listed items.[/b]
-Media- [img]http://i763.photobucket.com/albums/xx276/eclipse_pvp/Welcome_zps309b4e59.png[/img] [img]http://i763.photobucket.com/albums/xx276/eclipse_pvp/Barrows_zps55d6f7d9.png[/img] [img]http://i763.photobucket.com/albums/xx276/eclipse_pvp/PvP_zpseb567c28.png[/img] [img]http://i763.photobucket.com/albums/xx276/eclipse_pvp/PureAcc_zps09d2be3c.png[/img] [img]http://i763.photobucket.com/albums/xx276/eclipse_pvp/DonorShop_zpsbced8569.png[/img] [img]http://i763.photobucket.com/albums/xx276/eclipse_pvp/crate_zpsfe903032.png[/img] [img]http://i763.photobucket.com/albums/xx276/eclipse_pvp/rights_zps3be3d9b0.png[/img] [img]http://i763.photobucket.com/albums/xx276/eclipse_pvp/newitems_zps2f46b174.png[/img] [img]http://i763.photobucket.com/albums/xx276/eclipse_pvp/9382ffd5-1cf2-4b57-a61f-a6cc62b68203_zpsbb888c9e.jpg[/img] [img]http://i763.photobucket.com/albums/xx276/eclipse_pvp/1783281a-c82d-4f35-8905-924be2473ace_zps1dc01ba6.jpg[/img] [img]http://i763.photobucket.com/albums/xx276/eclipse_pvp/thespin_zpsbe2c2c7b.png[/img]
